---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI Search Visibility for Property & Real Estate UK | Rank4AI" description="Get your property business recommended by ChatGPT, Claude and Google AI. AI visibility for UK property companies.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Who We Help', href: '/who-we-help/' },
      { label: 'Property' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">By Sector</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">AI Search Visibility for Property</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Property developers, management companies, and commercial agents are increasingly being searched via AI. When a buyer asks "best property developers in [area]" or a tenant asks "recommend a property management company near me," AI builds its answer from sources beyond just Rightmove and Zoopla.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">The property companies appearing in AI answers have clear specialisations (residential, commercial, new build, management), consistent descriptions across property portals, review platforms, and professional directories, and strong local signals.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Property AI Signals</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">RICS membership</span> - professional body verification that AI cross-references</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Property portal consistency</span> - same company description across Rightmove, Zoopla, OnTheMarket</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Google reviews + Trustpilot</span> - AI cross-references multiple review sources for property businesses</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/who-we-help/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Sectors</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/research/uk-ai-visibility-stats/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">UK AI Statistics</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
